'''Fate Contract: Renewal''' is an [[Event]] in [[Version 4.4]].

==Event Details==
===Duration===
* 2026/07/24 12:00:00 (server time) - [[Version 4.6]] ends

===Requirements===
* [[Trailblaze Level]] ≥ 3

==Summary==
* During the event, Trailblazers can log in to the game to claim the limited 5-star collaboration character {{Character Intro|Gilgamesh}} or {{Character Intro|Archer}} and materials to build them to Lv. 60.

